OL,3,CStarmer says Gorton and Denton by-
OL,4,Celection result is 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has vowed to "keep on
OL,7,Ffighting" despite Labour's humiliating
OL,8,Fdefeat in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FThe prime minister faces intense
OL,12,Fpressure to shift his party to the
OL,13,Fleft or resign after Labour came third
OL,14,Fbehind Zack Polanski's Greens and
OL,15,FNigel Farage's Reform UK in the
OL,16,Fpreviously rock-solid Greater
OL,17,FManchester constituency.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@IO]
