OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772301852
OL,3,CStarmer says Gorton and Denton by-
OL,4,Celection result is 'very disappointing'
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters, he acknowledged
OL,7,Fit was a "disappointing" result and
OL,8,Fthat voters were "frustrated", but
OL,9,Finsisted he would carry on.
OL,11,FAsked if he had considered resigning,
OL,12,Fthe prime minister said: "I came into
OL,13,Fpolitics late in life to fight for
OL,14,Fchange for those people who need it.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
