OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772301852
OL,3,CStarmer says Gorton and Denton by-
OL,4,Celection result is 'very disappointing'
OL,6,F"I will keep on fighting for those
OL,7,Fpeople for as long as I've got breath
OL,8,Fin my body."
OL,10,FStarmer also pledged to "fight against
OL,11,Fextremes in politics" on both the left
OL,12,Fand the right that threatened to "tear
OL,13,Four country apart".
OL,15,FHannah Spencer, a councillor and
OL,16,Fplumber, emerged victorious for the
OL,17,FGreens with 14,980 votes ` a majority
OL,18,Fof 4,402 at Thursday's by-election.
OL,26,@tD@bOUuD@RO]
